---
title: Pea and Mushroom Rogan Josh with sprinkled scallion and fluffy rice
description: This slightly spicy rogan josh veggie curry features two vibrant veg, peas and mushrooms, which each bring their own unique elements to this abundant and nutritious dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W47_IE_IECLVV17714-2_Main__high-ba327bfe.jpg
